firewall.summary:

              * There are no vulnerability in term of service from the internal side of the firewall

external_result.summary:
=========General scan report========= 
              * The external firewall have 2 tcp and 1 udp port open
              * http (Apache httpd 2.4.58), https-alt (OPNsense ),  ntp,  are listening in the external ip
              * ICMP is blocked or filtered (ICMP packet to the external ip)
              * there are vulnerability (2) from the service open to public
